==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''singleton''' (plural: '''singletons''')
# (''playing cards'') A [[playing card]] that is the only one of its [[suit]] in a [[hand]], especially at [[bridge]]
# a [[single]] [[object]], especially one of a [[group]]
# (''computer science'') A [[w:design pattern (computer science)|design pattern]] to force a [[w:class (computer science)|class]] to have no more than one instance at any given time
# (''computer science'') A [[w:class (computer science)|class]] that may not be instantiated more than once at a time
# (''math'') [[set]] with just one element

